Playing Tic Tac Toe++ :- STEP 1:- Have the first player go First. STEP 2:- Have the second player go second. STEP 3:- Keep alternatting moves untill one players has drawn a row of three symbols or untill one can win. STEP 4:- Keep practicing.
Becoming an EXPERT in TicTacToe++ :- STEP 1:- Make the best first move. STEP 2:- React appropriately if the other player goes first. STEP 3:- Follow the "right,left,above,and below" strategy. STEP 4:- Use the three-corner strategy. STEP 5:- Play against a machine. STEP 6:- Take it to the next level.
Tipes For Play Tic Tac Toe++ :- SINGLE PLAYER :- Type "Computer" in textbox2 to play with Computer. MUILTI PLAYER :- You must specify the 'players' name before start the GAME!!! & textbox2 name anything except "Computer".
